    update(ThreadedAnvilChunkStorage chunkStorage)
    Update the states related to chunk tickets and chunk loading levels, which mainly involves three kind of updates: Add or remove PLAYER tickets when necessary. Update the expected loading states of chunks depending on their new levels. Special updates of chunks with PLAYER tickets added recently.
